{"tid":1722491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[九龍中計黨]建議唔好再死守poly","createTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T06:53:41.000Z","uid":210995,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"78798a4e95a0b611446211f30c8377ce9ffdf509","tid":1722491,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:29.000Z","msg":"Poly裡面已經有各式各樣既分化撚、捉鬼<br />\n成個氣候唔太明朗<br />\n似乎係班曱甴專登一日派幾隻輕輕撚下你<br />\n又得閒放下啲消息話已經有鬼入左黎等手足極度緊張<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結果？</span></strong><br />\n自然開始捉鬼 態度唔好 之後配合埋連登有人屌班手足冇禮貌而分化我地<br />\n<br />\n其實講左五個月架啦 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不督灰 不捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\nPoly唔同中大 易攻難守 <br />\n<br />\n而家港共咁玩係好聰明<br />\n因為而家已經成功lock死哂最前線嗰班𡃁仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔該心態上唔好再玩大學陣地 應守就守<br />\n難守就應棄 做啲更加有意義既野<br />\n唔好再死守啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fc5ab0ec016fbf74d6c9945e63b4d282b1a17578","tid":1722491,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:03:54.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"9c8512f8fe066364b4c99053810487d4bb0a2da7","tid":1722491,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5caa1b89badab8053d4356ce77f8eb5174f980e3","tid":1722491,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"其中一曱甴風向文<br />\n<br />\nPoly真係戇撚鳩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1721827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1721827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e2693b648300fb9f6cc1de3bfeade79bee629dcd","tid":1722491,"uid":210995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T02:06:33.000Z","m